    <user>anag_factory</user>
    <comment>- updated to 1.2.25.7
   see /usr/share/doc/packages/perl-Search-Xapian/Changes
  1.2.25.7  Wed Jun  3 22:45:01 UTC 2026
  	[Changes contributed by Olly Betts]
  	- README: Update status - there are not likely to be further releases.
  	- If the C++ compiler isn't found and g++ isn't installed, look for
  	  c++ - this means the build should work out of the box on systems
  	  such as FreeBSD where the default compiler is clang.  Reported by
  	  eserte12 (fixes #851).</comment>
    <requestid>1358712</requestid>
  </revision>
